media-player-info (3-1) experimental; urgency=low

  * Initial release. (Closes: #546967) This provides media player information
    in *.mpi files, the designated replacement for the former fdi files in a
    hal-free world.  Rhythmbox 0.12.4 uses these now.
  * configure: Add hack to hardcode udev_dir until our udev gets updated to
    a newer version which ships a pkg-config file.

 -- Martin Pitt <martin.pitt@ubuntu.com>  Thu, 27 Aug 2009 11:45:03 +0200
